       L1.
           ACCEPT TCPFPACIENTE
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 01
                   GO TO ROT-FIM.
           IF CPFPACIENTE = ZEROS
              MOVE " ** PREENCHA O CAMPO PARA PROSSEGUIR ** " TO MENS
              PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
              GO TO L1.
       L2.
