       ACE-001.
           DISPLAY (23, 12)"N=NOVO REGISTRO   A=ALTERAR   E=EXCLUIR"
           ACCEPT (23, 55) W-OPCAO
           IF W-OPCAO NOT = "N" AND W-OPCAO NOT = "A" 
